          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Experience world-class coaching and a safe, comfortable skating environment at our facility. Our team of certified and experienced coaches, many of whom have competed at the highest levels, offer personalized instruction for skaters of all ages and skill levels. Our fully stocked pro shop provides everything you need, from skate rentals and sharpening to a wide selection of equipment and apparel. We offer a variety of programs to cater to skaters of all abilities, from beginner classes to advanced training. To ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for everyone, we use a session-based ticket entry system, preventing overcrowding and providing ample space for skaters to enjoy the ice."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restriction: Thick socks and gloves are essential for comfortable and safe skating, especially for young children"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restriction: Smallest skates size is UK Kid's 8/EU Kid's 25/15cm and biggest skates size is UK 13/EU 48/31cm"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Dress code: Recommend wearing comfortable, warm clothing such as long-sleeved shirts, light jackets, and long pants to ensure both warmth and safety"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
